# 15. Failure Handling Strategy


External API failure:




External Service

↓

Integration Layer

↓

Retry Mechanism

↓

Fallback Response


Example:


GitHub API unavailable:


System shows:

"GitHub analysis temporarily unavailable"

instead of failing entire profile.



